<section id="docker">
<h3>Docker Containers</h3>

<p><strong>pyaction</strong>: A Docker container designed to support implementing Github 
Actions with Python. It consists of a python slim Docker image, additionally with curl, gpg, 
git, and the GitHub CLI.</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://actions.cicirello.org/pyaction/">Info page</a></li>
<li>Docker Hub: <a href="https://hub.docker.com/r/cicirello/pyaction"><img src="https://img.shields.io/docker/v/cicirello/pyaction?label=Docker%20Hub&logo=docker" alt="Docker Hub" height="20"></a></li>
